---
// 3 step panels for the How It Works section
---

<div class="steps__showcase reveal">

  <div class="steps__panel active" data-panel="0">
    <div class="steps__panel-info">
      <div class="steps__panel-icon steps__panel-icon--green">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><rect x="5" y="2" width="14" height="20" rx="2"/><line x1="12" y1="18" x2="12" y2="18"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="steps__panel-title">Phone Number Se Asaan Login</h3>
      <p class="steps__panel-desc">Koi form nahin, koi password nahin. Bas apna phone number daalein, OTP aaye — aur aap andar. 10 seconds se bhi kam mein shuru karein.</p>
      <ul class="steps__panel-features">
        <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary-600)" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>Koi registration form nahin</li>
        <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary-600)" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>Sirf phone number — OTP se login</li>
        <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary-600)" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>Shaffaf PKR qeematein — koi hidden charge nahin</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="steps__panel-phone">
      <div class="steps__phone-frame">
        <img src="/assets/screenshots/login-app.jpeg" alt="Ilaaj AI Login" width="320" height="693" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="steps__panel" data-panel="1">
    <div class="steps__panel-info">
      <div class="steps__panel-icon steps__panel-icon--blue">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="steps__panel-title">AI Se Freely Baat Karein</h3>
      <p class="steps__panel-desc">WhatsApp jaisi chat mein apni problem bata dein. AI sawaal poochta hai — sharm ki koi baat nahin, doosri taraf koi insaan nahin.</p>
      <ul class="steps__panel-features">
        <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary-600)" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>Urdu ya English — koi bhi bolein</li>
        <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary-600)" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>100% private — koi judge nahin karta</li>
        <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary-600)" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>AI symptoms samajh kar case banata hai</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="steps__panel-phone">
      <div class="steps__phone-frame">
        <img src="/assets/screenshots/chat-app.jpeg" alt="Ilaaj AI Chat" width="320" height="693" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="steps__panel" data-panel="2">
    <div class="steps__panel-info">
      <div class="steps__panel-icon steps__panel-icon--teal">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><path d="M16 13H8"/><path d="M16 17H8"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="steps__panel-title">Verified Prescription — 15-20 Min</h3>
      <p class="steps__panel-desc">Doctor 15-20 minute mein verify karta hai. Prescription aapke phone par — PDF download karein, kisi bhi pharmacy le jayein.</p>
      <ul class="steps__panel-features">
        <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary-600)" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>PDF format — download karein</li>
        <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary-600)" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>Kisi bhi pharmacy mein valid</li>
        <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary-600)" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>PMDC doctor ki seal aur signature</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="steps__panel-phone">
      <div class="steps__phone-frame">
        <img src="/assets/screenshots/prescription.jpeg" alt="Prescription" width="320" height="693" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
